Package org.grobid.trainer.sax

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChemicalClassNamesSaxParser
    This SAX parser simply records the chemical class name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
    ChemicalFormulasSaxParser
    This SAX parser simply records the chemical formula stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
    ChemicalLigandSaxParser
    This SAX parser simply records the chemical class name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
    ChemicalNameSaxParser
    This SAX parser simply records the chemical name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
    ChemicalSubstancesSaxParser
    This SAX parser simply records the chemical substance name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
    ChemicalWordsSaxParser
    This SAX parser process the list of words of a document and produce the labeled data based on stand off annotations.
    FieldExtractSaxHandler
    Utility SAX parser which extracts all the text content under a given TEI tag name or under a specified xml path.
    MPDL_METS_SaxParser
    SAX parser for the MPDL METS catalogue data.
    NLMHeaderSaxHandler
    SAX parser for the NLM XML format - the PubMed XML full text format.
    TEIAffiliationAddressSaxParser
    SAX parser for affiliation+address sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
    TEIAuthorSaxParser
    SAX parser for author sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
    TEICitationOpenEdition
    SAX parser for the TEI format for OpenEdition citation data.
    TEICitationSaxParser
    SAX parser for the XML format for citation data.
    TEIDateSaxParser
    SAX parser for author sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
    TEIEbookSaxParser
    SAX parser for the TEI format for fulltext data.
    TEIFulltextSaxParser
    SAX parser for the TEI format for fulltext data encoded for training.
    TEIHeaderSaxParser
    SAX parser for the TEI format header data encoded for training.
    TEIHeaderSaxParserOCRTraining
    SAX parser for the TEI format header data.
    TEIReferenceSegmenterSaxParser
    SAX parser for reference strings encoded in the TEI format data for training purposes.
    TEISegmentationSaxParser
    SAX parser for the TEI format for the training data for the segmentation model.
    WikiTextExtractSaxParser
    SAX parser for XML Wikipedia page articles (file .hgw.xml).
